OL,3,CCharity managers 'broken' after
OL,4,Cthousands stolen during break-in
OL,6,FA charity manager has been left
OL,7,F'distraught' after her community
OL,8,Fcentre was burgled and vandalised in
OL,9,FPaignton.
OL,11,FPolice are investigating the thefts
OL,12,Fwhich took place at the CentrePeace
OL,13,FCommunity Cafe overnight on 26 and 27
OL,14,FMay.
OL,16,FOfficers are searching for two men who
OL,17,Fthey believe are responsible for
OL,18,Fstealing #2,000 and causing more than
OL,19,F#10,000 worth of damage.
