OL,6,FCentrePeace offers a range of
OL,7,Fservices, from free workshops,
OL,8,Factivities and counselling to a
OL,9,Fcharity shop and a cafe selling
OL,10,Faffordable meals.
OL,12,FManager Dee Mulhall described the
OL,13,Fmoment she found the devastation: "I
OL,14,Fwalked upstairs and saw what they had
OL,15,Fdone. The place was trashed. It broke
OL,16,Fme. I was just distraught.
OL,18,F"I was mortified that they took money,
OL,19,Fbecause we're a charity. Everything we
OL,20,Fmake goes back into supporting the
OL,21,Flocal community.
