OL,6,F"The worst thing about it is now our
OL,7,Fregulars have nowhere to go. One man
OL,8,Fwho comes in every single day, just
OL,9,Flooked at me and said 'where am I
OL,10,Fsupposed to go now?' It's
OL,11,Fheartbreaking."
OL,13,FCentrePeace opened its doors in 2013
OL,14,Fand initially supported the homeless
OL,15,Fcommunity in Paignton. But over the
OL,16,Fyears, it has evolved into a large
OL,17,Fcommunity hub.
