OL,3,CCharity managers 'broken' after
OL,4,Cthousands stolen during break-in
OL,6,F15-year-old Fiona Akter started
OL,7,Fvolunteering at CentrePeace as part of
OL,8,Fher Duke of Edinburgh Award. But
OL,9,Fbecause she enjoyed it so much, has
OL,10,Fcontinued working for the charity.
OL,12,FFiona said: "It's just so sad. Why
OL,13,Fwould someone do this? It's a charity,
OL,14,Fa place which helps people every day.
OL,16,F"If we don't have good places like
OL,17,Fthis for people to go to, people won't
OL,18,Fsurvive. These places are needed."
