OL,6,FDee is slowly piecing the community
OL,7,Fcentre back together and has launched
OL,8,Fa crowdfunder to help pay for the
OL,9,Frepairs.
OL,11,FShe hopes CentrePeace will be able to
OL,12,Freopen soon, and thanks people for
OL,13,Ftheir kindness and offers of donations.
OL,15,FA Devon and Cornwall Police
OL,16,Fspokesperson said: "Officers are
OL,17,Finvestigating the burglaries and
OL,18,Fappealing to anyone who saw or heard
OL,19,Fanything suspicious to contact them.
